1
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:25,520
<i>Add five drops to his food daily.</i>

2
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,680
<i>Then, he'll suffer heart failure.</i>

3
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,120
<i>No matter how skilled the doctor is,</i>

4
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:30,600
<i>they won't be able to detect poison.</i>

5
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,160
Mr. Yai, don't eat yet.

6
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,280
Please wait for me.

7
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,640
Pin. I was so blind.

8
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:38,520
I chose the wrong woman.

9
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,600
<i>Let's give ourselves another chance.</i>
<i>Please, Pin.</i>

10
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,160
- Mr. Na, let me go.
- <i>Leave the area now.</i>

11
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:44,800
You aren't strong enough
to carry me, Pin. Go.

12
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,720
I've been coming back…

13
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,520
because I missed you.

14
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,880
You're crying again, Pin.

15
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:24,120
I have something to tell you too.

16
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:32,160
I no longer have feelings for Mr. Tatsana.

17
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,560
I don't believe you.

18
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,320
You're lying to me.

19
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:45,680
You sent food to Yai every day?

20
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,040
The medicine should have had
an effect by now.

21
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:50,920
But I delivered it
to Pin myself every evening.

22
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,800
You're not fooling me, are you, Un?

23
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,600
I've added so much of it.

24
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,240
Something should be happening to him.

25
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,560
- But I--
- Krong.

26
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,520
Have you heard?

27
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:05,000
- About what?
- Yai's sick right now.

28
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:07,480
I heard the workers say it's serious.

29
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,000
He can't even get out of bed.

30
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,480
Your medicine is really something.

31
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,240
Mr. Yai.

32
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,240
Wake up, Mr. Yai.

33
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,080
I'll wipe you down.

34
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,720
Do you still have a fever?

35
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,840
Or is it…

36
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,400
Mr. Yai.

37
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,880
Mr. Yai, are you okay?

38
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,520
Please answer me.

39
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,520
Mr. Yai, what's wrong?

40
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,280
I'm not dead yet.

41
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,560
Why weren't you answering me?

42
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:39,000
You made me really exhausted last night,
so my fever got worse than it was before.

43
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:44,080
I didn't do anything.

44
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:50,600
I had a fever, my head's split open,
and I had almost no energy.

45
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:54,840
If you told someone I was the one making
a move on you, who would believe it?

46
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:58,000
You were the one
who harassed me all night.

47
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,920
Mr. Yai, does your wound hurt?

48
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,440
I'm sorry.

49
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,200
You're brutal, Pin.

50
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,960
My whole body is sore because of you.

51
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:13,680
Wait until I recover,
and I'll get back at you big time.

52
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,240
I'm dizzy again.

53
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:22,040
The fever's probably coming back.

54
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,080
Take your medicine, then.

55
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:44,720
Madam?

56
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,400
Yeah, it's me.

57
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,320
You look like you've seen a ghost.

58
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,360
I'm here to check on Mr. Yai.

59
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,640
How is he feeling?

60
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,600
He's feeling better now.

61
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,760
Let me see him. Open the door.

62
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,560
You can't. Mr. Yai is asleep right now.

63
00:08:57,640 --> 00:09:01,160
Pin. Don't get cocky with me.

64
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,960
See? Look at your hands.

65
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:06,360
They're even rougher than my feet.

66
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:09,160
Even if you wear expensive clothes,

67
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:11,880
you can't hide your true nature as a maid.

68
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:15,720
I have to be cruel like you are
to be considered superior, right?

69
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:16,800
Pin.

70
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:20,440
I know what you're planning
to do to Mr. Yai.

71
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,520
I won't just stand there
and watch anymore.

72
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:25,480
Then go ahead. Tell your husband.

73
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:28,840
Tell him who's been the one
following my orders.

74
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:33,120
This time, I won't be
the only one going down.

75
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,080
Right?

76
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:40,440
Don't you want to know
how Mr. Na is doing right now?

77
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:45,760
He's about to be happily married.

78
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:51,240
What? Why? Why do you bring up Na?

79
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,560
Why don't you try calling Ms. On?

80
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:08,400
On. I couldn't reach Na.

81
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,600
Is he there with you? Can I talk to him?

82
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:14,760
Well, he's gone back to the farm.

83
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:17,200
Oh? Why did he come back?

84
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,520
What about the wedding?

85
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,520
We just had a little argument.

86
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:24,080
But if he still doesn't want
to come back and talk,

87
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:26,000
don't expect me to forgive him.

88
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,200
You know where Na is, don't you?

89
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:38,200
If you want to see him,
you must follow my terms only.

90
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:42,440
You dare to negotiate with me, Pin?

91
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,280
Mr. Na was complaining
about wanting to die.

92
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:49,480
If you don't hurry up,
you might never see him alive again.

93
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,800
Then tell me your terms.

94
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,800
Na?

95
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:40,240
Hey, wait, Na. Na!

96
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:42,240
I'm right here.

97
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:45,560
You're okay now. Open the door.

98
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:49,440
My life is ruined, Auntie.

99
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:52,200
I know everything now. Hey.

100
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:54,200
There are plenty of other wealthy women.

101
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,640
I'll find one for you.

102
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:58,760
I'm afraid.

103
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,680
They tried to trick me
into paying their debts.

104
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:05,520
What if they borrowed from loan sharks?

105
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:08,480
What if they come after me for the money?

106
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,440
Those people are brutal.

107
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:16,440
I'm… I'm scared, Auntie!

108
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,560
Hey, I'm here for you.

109
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:21,120
Don't be afraid. I can handle it.

110
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,840
Why am I so unlucky?

111
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,360
I wanna die, Auntie!

112
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,480
No! Hey.

113
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:35,600
I have a way to make you
a lot of money to start a new life

114
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:37,720
and also to get revenge on Yai.

115
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:40,520
You hate him, don't you?!

116
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:16,200
Don't think about wanting to die again.

117
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:27,120
Come in. I'm lying here naked, Pin.

118
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,400
Tatsanee?

119
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:51,760
Will you leave on your own,
or should I throw you out of the room?

120
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,840
Come on, bro.

121
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:56,000
I just want

122
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:59,120
- some warmth from you, that's all.
- Hey, hey.

123
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:02,760
I'll count to three. One, two…

124
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:04,680
Wait. Hold on!

125
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:17,240
Pin is cheating on you.

126
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:22,440
She rushed all the way to reignite
an old flame with Na at his hotel room.

127
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:29,120
I sent her.

128
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:32,160
She was just running an errand
for her husband.

129
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,760
Any other concerns?

130
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:56,880
You can't sleep, Mr. Yai?

131
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:00,200
Or are you still feeling sore?

132
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:13,120
I'm picturing our family.

133
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:18,880
You, me, and our children.

134
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:24,480
A family won't be complete with just that.

135
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:27,640
There has to be your side of the family

136
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:30,840
and my side of the family too.

137
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:40,800
My parents aren't around anymore.

138
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:47,040
But I'm not sure about yours.

139
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:53,440
We'll have to win over my mom.

140
00:15:55,880 --> 00:16:00,320
If you're not comfortable doing it,
I'll do it myself.

141
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:08,840
I'll do it too.

142
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:15,800
Are you ready to forgive
everything my mom did

143
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:19,200
and love her like I do?

144
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:23,120
Not only your mom.

145
00:16:23,640 --> 00:16:25,840
I'll forgive everyone,

146
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:28,640
including Madam Krongsuk and Na.

147
00:16:29,680 --> 00:16:30,640
Even my dad.

148
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:34,880
I'll leave my terrible childhood behind.

149
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:40,320
The past has hurt you, Mr. Yai.

150
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:43,720
I'm glad you can see that.

151
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:49,320
Are you sure you want to build
a new family with me?

152
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:01,200
Yes. Our little family.

153
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:05,960
I'm so glad.

154
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:08,520
I haven't washed my hair yet.

155
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:12,560
You already smell good all over, Pin.

156
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:16,599
Your neck, your shoulders…

157
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:19,040
…your arms.

158
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:21,760
Or… Right here.

159
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:22,760
Mr. Yai.

160
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:25,640
I don't smell that good.

161
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:29,240
- I'll smell you myself.
- Mr. Yai.

162
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:41,280
Pin? What are you doing
sitting in the dark?

163
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,760
Where's the medicine from this vial?

164
00:17:54,840 --> 00:17:56,280
I drank it all.

165
00:17:58,040 --> 00:18:00,000
Are you crazy? Do you want to die?!

166
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:03,720
- Let's go to the hospital now.
- So you admit it's poison?

167
00:18:10,320 --> 00:18:12,560
You've been putting this
in Mr. Yai's food every day,

168
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,960
as Madam ordered.

169
00:18:18,120 --> 00:18:19,760
You don't need to say anything.

170
00:18:21,760 --> 00:18:23,200
Let's just say I know everything.

171
00:18:25,120 --> 00:18:28,800
I only came to tell you
that I love Mr. Yai.

172
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,760
And if you try to kill him,

173
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,480
I will die first.

174
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:38,440
But Yai is trying
to kill Madam and Mr. Na!

175
00:18:39,040 --> 00:18:40,400
Madam lied to you.

176
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:43,760
Mr. Yai doesn't even know where Mr. Na is.

177
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:48,080
If you stop doing
what she tells you to do,

178
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:51,960
I'll give her everything she asks for.

179
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:54,360
If you don't,

180
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:58,640
I'll be forced to turn my back on her.

181
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,640
You don't have a fever anymore.

182
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:17,960
But the doctor said
you still can't go out in the sun,

183
00:19:18,040 --> 00:19:19,440
or the fever will come back.

184
00:19:20,040 --> 00:19:24,560
Once you're feeling better, you'll need
to get a brain scan like he mentioned.

185
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:28,440
Can't we just lie down
and cuddle some more?

186
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:30,080
I'm still dizzy.

187
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:33,520
Jin isn't feeling well.

188
00:19:33,600 --> 00:19:35,000
I'm going to check on her.

189
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:38,840
But I'll be back to have lunch with you.

190
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:52,840
Okay then.

191
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:55,000
But if you take too long,

192
00:19:55,080 --> 00:19:56,680
I might chat with some other girls

193
00:19:56,760 --> 00:19:59,520
to keep myself entertained, alright?

194
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:04,800
So fierce.

195
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:27,280
I told you Pin is lovely.

196
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:28,600
She's a woman of her word.

197
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:34,440
I didn't expect you
to do this much for Mr. Yai.

198
00:20:35,040 --> 00:20:36,880
Money is not everything.

199
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:41,000
If it can buy peace for my family,

200
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:42,440
I won't hesitate to use it.

201
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:46,680
This is all my dowry money.

202
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:49,880
I hope you'll do as you promised, Madam.

203
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:51,640
Of course.

204
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,320
Once I get the money,

205
00:20:53,840 --> 00:20:57,480
I'll take Na and Nee away
from Paisal Farm immediately.

206
00:20:57,560 --> 00:20:59,360
And never come back.

207
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:09,160
I didn't think
you'd actually believe what I said.

208
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:11,880
Oh, you're so naive.

209
00:21:14,120 --> 00:21:16,280
Then don't ever think
you'll get this money.

210
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:23,280
Do you think I'll be satisfied
with just this money? Huh?

211
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:28,200
All of Yai's inheritance that should be
my family's, that's what I want.

212
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:31,320
Mr. Yai is willing to forgive you,

213
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:34,040
but you don't even want to change.

214
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:39,120
Don't pretend to be a saint
in an ideal world.

215
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:41,360
Why did you even marry Yai?

216
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:43,560
Because you love him?

217
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:45,320
I wouldn't believe you in a million years.

218
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:47,840
You wanted to be the farm owner's wife

219
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:50,960
because you've been wanting
to step on us for a long time.

220
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:54,600
And no matter how bad, disgusting,
or despicable he is, you don't care.

221
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:56,600
Mr. Yai is not a bad person.

222
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:59,880
Otherwise,
you wouldn't be standing here right now.

223
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:04,920
Then, if he dies today,

224
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:07,440
he'll probably become an angel in Heaven.

225
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:09,600
Today?

226
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:12,840
What does that mean?

227
00:22:14,080 --> 00:22:18,360
You must think I'm too stupid
to keep up with your game, huh?

228
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:48,760
Your mom wouldn't trust you
more than she trusts me,

229
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:53,640
because I know her better than you do.

230
00:23:00,360 --> 00:23:03,640
Yai tied Mr. Na up, starved him,

231
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:07,880
and threatened to kill him
if Madam didn't agree to leave the farm.

232
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:14,120
Only you can help
Mr. Na and Madam, Aunt Un.

233
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:30,320
Mr. Yai, I made you some soup.

234
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:32,840
I heard you're tired of rice porridge.

235
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:36,360
He must be lying there in misery

236
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:38,680
and about to die by now.

237
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:43,160
And your mom will be taken in
as Yai's murderer.

238
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:46,320
Then, no matter how much
the police grill her,

239
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:49,280
she'll never rat me out.

240
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:53,880
I should have known from the start

241
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:57,160
that I couldn't keep up
with your deceptions.

242
00:23:58,360 --> 00:24:00,960
But I didn't think you'd be so cruel,

243
00:24:01,040 --> 00:24:03,760
heartless, and vile like this.

244
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:04,800
Enough of this.

245
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,760
Where are you going? Give it here.

246
00:24:14,280 --> 00:24:17,160
Na, help me. Take the bag from her now.

247
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:20,280
Mr. Na. Please don't hurt me.

248
00:24:20,840 --> 00:24:21,920
Mr. Na…

249
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:24,360
You need to stop Madam
from doing more evil things.

250
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,120
Pin.

251
00:24:28,320 --> 00:24:31,040
You're talking too much, Pin.

252
00:24:31,120 --> 00:24:33,560
If I leave you alive,
it will only cause me more trouble.

253
00:24:37,600 --> 00:24:38,560
No, Auntie.

254
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:39,560
Move aside, Na.

255
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,400
It'll only be trouble if we let her go.

256
00:24:44,800 --> 00:24:45,960
Pin.

257
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:50,840
I love her.

258
00:24:52,320 --> 00:24:54,480
I'll never let you do anything to her.

259
00:24:58,560 --> 00:24:59,520
Madam.

260
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:25,280
How did you survive?

261
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,640
Jin isn't feeling well.

262
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:33,320
I'm going to check on her.

263
00:25:34,120 --> 00:25:37,120
But I'll be back to have lunch with you.

264
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:41,200
I'll put it here.

265
00:25:41,840 --> 00:25:43,000
So fierce.

266
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:49,080
I'll follow Pin.

267
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:50,280
You keep an eye on Aunt Un.

268
00:25:50,360 --> 00:25:52,560
I want to catch her in the act.

269
00:25:54,360 --> 00:25:55,200
So yesterday,

270
00:25:56,680 --> 00:26:00,560
you already knew that
I had gone to see Mr. Na?

271
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:05,960
I said I would forgive them
so you wouldn't leave me.

272
00:26:06,040 --> 00:26:09,040
But you were planning to run away
with them with all that money?

273
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:13,240
I withdrew the dowry money

274
00:26:13,320 --> 00:26:16,720
- because I wanted to--
- Pin offered

275
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:18,720
to give Na the money herself.

276
00:26:19,320 --> 00:26:23,240
When she found out that
Na was breaking up with Onsa-ang,

277
00:26:23,320 --> 00:26:25,720
she wanted to run away with him.

278
00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:27,360
Stop, Madam.

279
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:31,000
How much more evil do you need to be?

280
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:35,360
I tried to stop her
from doing anything wrong to you.

281
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:39,400
But she said she only loved Na

282
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,680
yet married you

283
00:26:42,080 --> 00:26:43,240
because she wanted money.

284
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:46,000
Mr. Na.

285
00:26:47,320 --> 00:26:49,200
You were standing right here.

286
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:51,160
You heard everything Madam said to me.

287
00:26:52,320 --> 00:26:54,480
You need to step up and tell the truth.

288
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:58,120
Don't just hide behind your aunt.

289
00:26:58,200 --> 00:27:00,000
Don't make me ask again!

290
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,880
The truth is…

291
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:25,800
We love each other.

292
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:30,240
Pin wants a divorce,
but she's afraid you'd hurt her.

293
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:33,520
You asshole.

294
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:35,520
Pin.

295
00:27:36,040 --> 00:27:38,960
That's enough! All of you will die here.

296
00:27:39,040 --> 00:27:43,040
Hey, if you dare touch Na again,
I'll fight you to the death!

297
00:28:18,240 --> 00:28:19,880
- Have you found it?
- No.

298
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:21,000
No.

299
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:21,960
Let's look somewhere else.

300
00:28:23,360 --> 00:28:26,160
- Let go of me! I don't wanna go.
- Come on, this way. Hold her.

301
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:27,200
Hurry. Follow me.

302
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:29,040
- Waan, let me go.
- Come here.

303
00:28:29,120 --> 00:28:30,320
Come on.

304
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:32,960
- Oh, my. Hurry up. Faster.
- Don't move.

305
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:34,560
I said don't move.

306
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:37,280
- Don't let go.
- Waan, let go of me now!

307
00:28:40,040 --> 00:28:41,000
Pan.

308
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:45,160
You snake woman.

309
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:49,400
How are things here?

310
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:51,640
I kept an eye on Aunt Un as you ordered.

311
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:57,200
But I didn't expect your mother
to be this cruel.

312
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:20,000
Mr. Yai, I made you some soup.

313
00:29:20,080 --> 00:29:21,800
I heard you're tired of rice porridge.

314
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:31,720
Yai's going after your daughter
to settle things.

315
00:29:32,800 --> 00:29:37,200
You probably need
to eat this soup yourself.

316
00:29:39,360 --> 00:29:40,560
What are you afraid of?

317
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,440
Why won't you eat it?

318
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:44,840
Noi!

319
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:45,880
Yes?

320
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:48,840
Lock Aunt Un in here.

321
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:51,240
If she escapes,

322
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:52,280
you're fired.

323
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:58,520
I think you'd better ask Pin.

324
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:00,800
She was afraid that
once she ran away with Na,

325
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:04,840
you would hunt her down,
so she tried to take your life first.

326
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:09,000
Admit it, Pin,
so your mom won't get in trouble.

327
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:20,640
Now I understand why my dad suddenly
lost muscle strength and couldn't walk.

328
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:22,160
It's because you all drugged him.

329
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,000
Mr. Yai.

330
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,520
Auntie.

331
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:35,720
Piak, what did you find?

332
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,520
We searched Madam's room

333
00:30:39,360 --> 00:30:40,760
but didn't find any poison.

334
00:30:44,520 --> 00:30:49,840
There's no evidence,
which means I'm still innocent.

335
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:51,840
I'll search Pinanong's room.

336
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:03,960
I didn't let Aunt Un out! She hit me.

337
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:06,320
All of you, let Madam go right now.

338
00:31:07,040 --> 00:31:09,360
It was me who poisoned you, Mr. Yai.

339
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,840
Madam wasn't involved.

340
00:31:15,280 --> 00:31:17,200
Pan, go search right now.

341
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:18,720
Yeah.

342
00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:21,000
No need to search.

343
00:31:26,240 --> 00:31:28,680
The medicine is in the bedroom,
dressing table drawer.

344
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:30,920
The key's in my bag.

345
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:52,280
Come with me,
so you can see it with your own eyes.

346
00:31:53,120 --> 00:31:56,040
Win, go be the witness.

347
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:57,720
Yes.

348
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:18,760
You found it?

349
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,480
- Piak!
- Hey, hey!

350
00:32:33,760 --> 00:32:35,160
Na, Nee, run!

351
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:45,720
Check if anyone's hurt. Uncle Win.

352
00:32:46,280 --> 00:32:47,880
- Madam…
- Mom.

353
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:53,520
- Mom. What's wrong, Mom?
- Are you okay?

354
00:32:56,800 --> 00:32:57,840
Go!

355
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:00,040
Nee.

356
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,120
Go to the parking lot!

357
00:33:09,720 --> 00:33:12,920
No, no! Don't shoot! I surrender!

358
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,360
We surrender.

359
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:18,960
Mr. Paisal took you all in,
sheltered you, fed you.

360
00:33:19,600 --> 00:33:20,760
But you chose to betray him.

361
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:24,680
You all deserve to die.

362
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:28,160
Uncle Pload! No, Uncle Pload.

363
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:30,040
Mr. Yai. Step aside.

364
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:37,040
We've been far too kind to them.

365
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:42,360
Krong! Get in!

366
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:44,920
Teera! Let's go. Hurry.

367
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:45,960
Hey, stop!

368
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:47,880
Uncle Pload, wait. No, stop!

369
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:55,080
Stop! Don't shoot!

370
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,640
You'll hit someone by mistake.

371
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:58,280
It'd be a mess if someone died.

372
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:10,440
Guys, go get them.

373
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:11,840
Yes, Boss.

374
00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:39,440
Are we going to die, Auntie?

375
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:42,239
No. I won't let you die.

376
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:43,679
Teera, step on it.

377
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:53,800
Mr. Tong, I'll find the money
to pay off the debt.

378
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:55,320
Please don't take my land deed.

379
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:00,480
Back off!

380
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:04,040
Mr. Tong! Mr. Tong, I beg you.

381
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:06,680
Go. Beat him up.

382
00:35:35,440 --> 00:35:37,240
Hurry up, Krong. Hurry.

383
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,640
Keep your head down.

384
00:36:02,480 --> 00:36:04,280
Help! Help! I'm being robbed!

385
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:06,080
Is that Madam Krongsuk, Boss?

386
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,680
- Help! Help!
- Stop, stop.

387
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:11,880
Help. I'm being robbed.

388
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:13,600
Please help me! Mr. Tong?!

389
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:19,080
Pload of Padang Besar's gang
is coming for you and me.

390
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:25,360
Fire back at them! Hey!

391
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:32,800
- Get in.
- What?

392
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:34,160
- Help us.
- Hey, what the hell?

393
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:47,640
Go!

394
00:36:47,720 --> 00:36:49,680
Let's go! Go.

395
00:36:56,440 --> 00:37:00,520
We're lucky Pan called me
and told me everything.

396
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:03,760
Otherwise,
I wouldn't have made it in time.

397
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:08,480
I'll regret for the rest of my life

398
00:37:09,040 --> 00:37:11,200
that I couldn't protect you.

399
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:17,600
This time, that Madam Krongsuk
will have to pay.

400
00:37:20,040 --> 00:37:20,960
Phong.

401
00:37:21,560 --> 00:37:23,240
Drag them in here. Go.

402
00:37:23,320 --> 00:37:26,720
Well, our men were about to catch them,

403
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:28,120
but some guys came to save them.

404
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:29,480
I don't know who they were.

405
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:32,560
One of our men was injured,
so I brought him to the hospital first.

406
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:34,080
How is he doing?

407
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:37,120
The bullet just grazed him,
nothing serious.

408
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:40,360
Go find out who they are

409
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:42,880
and where that madam is hiding.

410
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:45,160
Mow them down with M16s.

411
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:46,840
- Go.
- Yes, Boss.

412
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:51,440
Dad, please calm down.

413
00:37:54,280 --> 00:37:57,400
So what should we do with Pin and Aunt Un?

414
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:03,920
Do you remember the promise
you made to me, Mr. Yai?

415
00:38:08,240 --> 00:38:10,480
I'll allow you to marry Pinanong.

416
00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:14,560
But first, you must promise me

417
00:38:15,520 --> 00:38:19,480
that if I ever find out that this woman

418
00:38:19,560 --> 00:38:21,840
is working with Madam Krongsuk,

419
00:38:22,640 --> 00:38:25,360
you must cut ties

420
00:38:25,960 --> 00:38:28,960
and divorce Pinanong right away.

421
00:38:29,680 --> 00:38:31,160
Of course, Uncle.

422
00:38:35,160 --> 00:38:36,160
I'll divorce her.

423
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:39,800
You can do whatever
you see fit with that woman.

424
00:38:47,200 --> 00:38:51,280
I don't think Yai believes
Pin poisoned him.

425
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,480
He's just salty about Na.

426
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:55,000
You two are the same.

427
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:56,200
You're this way because of women.

428
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:58,040
I'll just castrate you all.

429
00:38:58,120 --> 00:39:00,880
Dad, are you hangry or something?

430
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:02,040
You're taking it out on everyone.

431
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:04,480
You think I can't see through you?

432
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:07,040
Don't even think about it.

433
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:10,960
If you're already thinking, then stop.

434
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:12,280
Wake up from that dream.

435
00:39:21,720 --> 00:39:25,400
Noi, go invite Mr. Yai
to come eat with us.

436
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:28,360
Mr. Yai's not in his room.

437
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:34,040
Hey, open the door right now.

438
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:35,480
I want to see Yai.

439
00:39:35,560 --> 00:39:38,720
Bring him here. Where is Yai?! Open up!

440
00:39:40,120 --> 00:39:40,960
Open up!

441
00:39:58,080 --> 00:40:00,800
Pin, how did the medicine
end up in your room?

442
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:11,960
Where's the medicine from this vial?

443
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:13,920
I drank it all.

444
00:40:16,240 --> 00:40:18,760
I planned to keep that medicine

445
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,640
and wait for a chance to expose Madam

446
00:40:21,200 --> 00:40:23,560
if she still wouldn't leave the farm.

447
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:26,080
But I never imagined

448
00:40:26,160 --> 00:40:29,480
that you wouldn't do what I asked.

449
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:35,400
As you're so loyal and grateful to Madam
without caring what's right or wrong,

450
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:39,320
I had to jump into the fire myself.

451
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:42,600
Are you satisfied now?

452
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:48,280
I didn't think it'd end up like this.

453
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:51,080
But Madam got away.

454
00:40:51,160 --> 00:40:52,600
She'll come back to help us.

455
00:40:52,680 --> 00:40:55,320
Madam is evil, Mom.

456
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:58,320
She has been using you.

457
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:00,880
Why can't you see it?

458
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:06,040
Pin, Yai hurt Madam first,

459
00:41:06,120 --> 00:41:08,160
so she had to do this.

460
00:41:08,240 --> 00:41:10,640
You're the one
who's blindly infatuated with him.

461
00:41:11,160 --> 00:41:12,520
Let me ask you honestly.

462
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:16,280
I really want to know.

463
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:19,920
How could you kill someone for her?

464
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:24,640
Is that how far you must go
to repay her kindness?

465
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:32,880
You'll never understand me, Pin.

466
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:37,000
Why wouldn't I understand?

467
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:42,880
The "gratitude" that acts
as a collar chaining you down

468
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:45,440
is chaining me down too.

469
00:41:55,120 --> 00:41:58,960
But… I didn't think
you'd take the fall for me.

470
00:41:59,880 --> 00:42:02,520
Fine. From now on,

471
00:42:02,600 --> 00:42:05,360
you don't have to repay
anything to me anymore.

472
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:06,920
Don't do it.

473
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:10,400
Just tell the truth, Pin. Just say it!

474
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:16,800
Mr. Yai won't trust me anymore.

475
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:22,280
My love is all ruined.

476
00:42:55,600 --> 00:42:57,400
Don't hurt my daughter.

477
00:43:00,160 --> 00:43:01,200
Piak!

478
00:43:02,200 --> 00:43:03,200
Mr. Yai.

479
00:43:03,920 --> 00:43:04,760
Pin.

480
00:43:08,200 --> 00:43:09,240
Where's my wife?

481
00:43:11,600 --> 00:43:13,720
Piak, what happened?

482
00:43:14,320 --> 00:43:16,080
A man in black barged in to take Pin away.

483
00:43:16,160 --> 00:43:17,600
He took my gun too.

484
00:43:17,680 --> 00:43:19,400
Where did he take my wife?

485
00:43:20,360 --> 00:43:21,280
That way.

486
00:43:22,680 --> 00:43:24,640
Hey, Mr. Yai. Wait.

487
00:43:25,280 --> 00:43:26,200
Mr. Yai…

488
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:31,520
Win, gather all our men on the farm

489
00:43:31,600 --> 00:43:34,560
and search everywhere
for a man in black and Pinanong.

490
00:43:34,640 --> 00:43:36,560
Don't let them escape.

491
00:43:36,640 --> 00:43:38,360
Yes. Let's go.

492
00:43:39,160 --> 00:43:41,040
Phong, come with me.

493
00:43:42,760 --> 00:43:43,960
Let's go.

494
00:43:48,320 --> 00:43:50,920
- Aunt Un.
- Mom. Mom.

495
00:43:53,600 --> 00:43:54,760
Pin, take Aunt Un and run.

496
00:43:54,840 --> 00:43:56,000
What about you?

497
00:43:56,080 --> 00:43:57,920
I can take care of myself.

498
00:43:58,000 --> 00:44:00,000
Just get Aunt Un out of here, now.

499
00:44:08,960 --> 00:44:11,040
Let's go, Mom. Come on.

500
00:44:20,800 --> 00:44:23,640
Just a little further, Mom. Mom.

501
00:44:23,720 --> 00:44:25,720
Mom. What's wrong, Mom?

502
00:44:25,800 --> 00:44:28,960
Mom. Mom.

503
00:44:29,800 --> 00:44:31,880
Mom! Mom.

504
00:44:51,720 --> 00:44:53,320
I'll defeat you.

505
00:44:54,880 --> 00:44:56,040
You're just a weakling.

506
00:45:12,800 --> 00:45:16,640
If you don't want Pin anymore,
just let her go.

507
00:45:17,960 --> 00:45:19,400
Stay away from my wife.

508
00:45:36,600 --> 00:45:38,040
Hang in there, Mom.

509
00:45:38,920 --> 00:45:40,240
Hang in there.

510
00:45:58,960 --> 00:46:03,600
Mom. Breathe, Mom. Breathe, okay?

511
00:46:04,160 --> 00:46:05,240
Come on.

512
00:46:06,640 --> 00:46:09,160
Try to sit up. Are you okay?

513
00:46:11,560 --> 00:46:12,520
Slowly.

514
00:46:13,080 --> 00:46:15,640
Jom! Jom!

515
00:46:16,240 --> 00:46:17,800
Mom's heart condition is acting up!

516
00:46:18,480 --> 00:46:19,560
Aunt Un…

517
00:46:25,760 --> 00:46:27,720
Why didn't you tell me
you're carrying my baby?

518
00:46:28,480 --> 00:46:31,000
The baby in Pin's womb is mine.

519
00:46:31,600 --> 00:46:32,800
<i>Let's get the divorce.</i>

520
00:46:32,880 --> 00:46:35,760
Even if you're not pregnant,
I was divorcing you anyway.

521
00:46:35,840 --> 00:46:37,720
I won't waste my time on someone like you.

522
00:46:37,800 --> 00:46:39,000
See for yourself, Aunt Un.

523
00:46:39,080 --> 00:46:42,640
Your blind love and gratitude

524
00:46:42,720 --> 00:46:44,480
<i>are destroying everyone's lives,</i>

525
00:46:44,560 --> 00:46:46,080
including your own daughter's.

526
00:46:46,960 --> 00:46:48,760
Mr. Tong, I need your help.

527
00:47:30,040 --> 00:47:32,240
Subtitle translation by: Anan Pratchayakul
